Package net.rim.device.api.io.parser.rss.event

Class Summary
CompleteRSSChannelEvent This event is posted by the RSSParser when a new RSSChannel finishes parsing.
CompleteRSSDocumentEvent This event is posted by an RSSParser when an RSS document is finished parsing.
NewRSSChannelEvent This event is posted by an RSSParser when a new channel is detected in an RSS document.
NewRSSItemEvent This event is posted by an RSSParser when a new item is parsed in a RSS document.
RSSErrorEvent This event is posted by an RSSParser when an error is encountered in an RSS document.
RSSEvent Base class for all RSS events.
